    "created_at": "2016-11-07T07:18:12Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-11-07T07:18:12Z",
    "body": "You can create `AtomHostResolver` class that will behave like [net::MappedHostResolver](https://cs.chromium.org/chromium/src/net/dns/mapped_host_resolver.h?q=mapped_&sq=package:chromium&l=1) , and provide callback mechanism similar to `AtomCertVerifier`. Also need to provide a mechanism where [brightray](https://github.com/electron/brightray/blob/master/browser/url_request_context_getter.cc#L203) can accept custom host resolver from embedder. You can look at how `AtomCertVerifier` was worked out.\n"
