    "body": "https://cs.chromium.org/chromium/src/net/dns/dns_config_service_posix.cc?l=502\r\n... dns_config->nameservers.push_back(ipe);...\r\nMaybe change this line to push back \"127.0.0.1\" or the dns server ip from \"--dns-server\"\r\n\r\n```\r\nIPAddress dns;\r\nIPEndPoint ipe;\r\nif (dns.AssignFromIPLiteral(\"127.0.0.1\"))\r\n{\r\n        ipe=IPEndPoint(dns, 53);\r\n}\r\ndns_config->nameservers.push_back(ipe);\r\n```"
  },
