    "updated_at": "2016-11-13T05:52:31Z",
    "body": "In my opinion, modifying ns_config->nameservers.push_back(get dns from command line arg --dns-server) will enable us business app developers to use our company's DNS server to avoid using our client users pollutted DNS. It's important not to use polluted DNS for business apps.\n"
